title: The Ultimate Gear Guide - Holiday Edition 2013
description:
The Ultimate Gear Guide - Holiday Edition 2013

196 Pages | HQ PDF | English | 39 MB 


Brought to you in conjunction with Guitar Player, Bass Player, Electronic Musician and KeyBoard Magazines.  Find the best gear for gift giving this holiday season, or treat yourself to the presents you deserve!   This years guide features hundreds of awesome gifts for musicians.  From guitars, basses, amps, keyboards, ukuleles, mandolins, banjos, recording and live-performance gear, effects, accessories and much more!
